        <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 mb-2">Are Costco hot dogs gluten free?</h3>
        <p class="text-gray-700">The hot dog meat itself does not contain gluten ingredients, but it is served in a wheat bun. Cross-contamination in the food court is likely.</p>
